{
    "version": 5,
    "bundle": "VBH2ZUACYTWRZJVDKQ7MD56DTP7JQJ45",
    "type": "story",
    "storyId": "801070001",
    "title": "教えてやろうか？",
    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "ある休日のこと――\r\n息抜きに外でランチをすることにしたのだが、\nメニューには難しい横文字ばかり並んでいる。",
            "enText": "One day on holiday - I decided to have lunch \nout to relax, but the menu was full of \ndifficult alphabets.",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "origClipLength": 115,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "（何がなんだか……）",
                    "enText": "(What's that?…)",
                    "nextBlock": 2
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 4521693756036008683,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "？？？",
            "enName": "???",
            "jpText": "へぇ、\r\nフレンチには慣れてないって顔だな。",
            "enText": "Well, you look like you're \nnot used to French food.",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 73,
            "pathId": -5571793348488211879,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "隣のテーブルから声がかけられたので\r\n振り返ると――",
            "enText": "I turned to look when I heard a voice from \nthe table next to mine.",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 78,
            "pathId": 310419032549920473,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シリウスシンボリ",
            "enName": "Sirius Symboli",
            "jpText": "メニュー、わからねぇんだろ？\r\n教えてやろうか。",
            "enText": "You don't know the menu, \ndo you? I'll show you.",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "origClipLength": 76,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "いいのか？",
                    "enText": "Are you sure?",
                    "nextBlock": 5
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "いいの？",
                    "enText": "Are you sure?",
                    "nextBlock": 5
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 166,
                    "pathId": -5109757050261768494
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 164,
                    "pathId": 2328537586028351543
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -697904461256863833,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シリウスシンボリ",
            "enName": "Sirius Symboli",
            "jpText": "ああ。ただし、私は教えるだけ。\r\nうまい食事にありつけるかはアンタ次第だ。",
            "enText": "Oh, yes. But I'm only going to \nteach you. It's up to you to make \nsure you get a good meal.",
            "nextBlock": 6,
            "origClipLength": 93,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 85,
                    "pathId": 304399811750297729
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 104,
                    "pathId": 6605475885010079908
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1109646306831635691,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "どこか含みのある言葉だ。\r\n教えを乞うべきだろうか……？",
            "enText": "It's a word with a certain connotation. \nShould I ask for help?…?",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "origClipLength": 81,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "自力で頑張る",
                    "enText": "Work hard on your own",
                    "nextBlock": 7
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "教えてもらう",
                    "enText": "Learn from us",
                    "nextBlock": 18
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 92,
                    "pathId": -5190010803357112993
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 92,
                    "pathId": 8269791791504330533
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 481892736558105472,
            "blockIdx": 6
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シリウスシンボリ",
            "enName": "Sirius Symboli",
            "jpText": "あっそ。じゃ、頑張れよ。\r\n上手くいくといいが。",
            "enText": "Oh, yeah. Well, good luck with \nthat. I hope it works out.",
            "nextBlock": 8,
            "origClipLength": 76,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 37,
                    "pathId": -4779889580318988545
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 87,
                    "pathId": 5437213782015056780
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -904088805881587279,
            "blockIdx": 7
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "しかし、自力で料理を頼んでみたところ――",
            "enText": "But when I ordered the food on my own—",
            "nextBlock": 9,
            "origClipLength": 71,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 82,
                    "pathId": -3116601755164053408
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 82,
                    "pathId": -4271197304017270245
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1542579108849854543,
            "blockIdx": 8
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シリウスシンボリ",
            "enName": "Sirius Symboli",
            "jpText": "オイオイ、全部野菜料理かよ！\r\nアンタ、持ってるな？",
            "enText": "Oh, come on, it's all vegetable food! \nYou've got it, haven't you?",
            "nextBlock": 10,
            "origClipLength": 78,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "やってしまった……",
                    "enText": "I've done it…",
                    "nextBlock": 10
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "やっちゃった……",
                    "enText": "I've done it…",
                    "nextBlock": 10
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 175,
                    "pathId": -7410304409376079484
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 187,
                    "pathId": 5083064466428816847
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5079931974669023454,
            "blockIdx": 9
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シリウスシンボリ",
            "enName": "Sirius Symboli",
            "jpText": "そんな悲しそうな顔するなって。\r\n食事は楽しむもんだろうが。",
            "enText": "Don't look so sad. You're supposed \nto enjoy your meal.",
            "nextBlock": 11,
            "origClipLength": 84,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 66,
                    "pathId": -8588586889222548212
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 95,
                    "pathId": 4978448269187841356
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8340781416694067672,
            "blockIdx": 10
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シリウスシンボリ",
            "enName": "Sirius Symboli",
            "jpText": "仕方ねえ、ちょっと手伝ってやる。\r\nほら、皿貸しな。",
            "enText": "No choice, I'll help you. Here, \ngive me your plate.",
            "nextBlock": 12,
            "origClipLength": 78,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 34,
                    "pathId": 6006754358026503878
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 89,
                    "pathId": -4949317339815241838
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5525125363896434601,
            "blockIdx": 11
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シリウスシンボリ",
            "enName": "Sirius Symboli",
            "jpText": "完食、と。\r\nそれなりにうまかったが――",
            "enText": "A complete meal. It was good, but…",
            "nextBlock": 13,
            "origClipLength": 71,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 151,
                    "pathId": -2346658987858255651
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 172,
                    "pathId": 8189415126643995164
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -656165745446888564,
            "blockIdx": 12
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シリウスシンボリ",
            "enName": "Sirius Symboli",
            "jpText": "野菜ばかりじゃつまらねぇ。食べ足りねぇ。\r\nなあ、アンタもそうは思わないか？",
            "enText": "It's boring to eat only vegetables. Not \nenough to eat. Don't you think so, too?",
            "nextBlock": 14,
            "origClipLength": 94,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "え？",
                    "enText": "Huh?",
                    "nextBlock": 14
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 52,
                    "pathId": -6634046836802935056
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 105,
                    "pathId": -3893461367011512693
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1285520697167554417,
            "blockIdx": 13
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シリウスシンボリ",
            "enName": "Sirius Symboli",
            "jpText": "たとえば今、目の前にいて……\r\n柔らかそうで――",
            "enText": "For example, I'm in front of you right \nnow. … It looks soft and—",
            "nextBlock": 15,
            "origClipLength": 76,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 80,
                    "pathId": -5840896170400306519
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 87,
                    "pathId": 8628465791273051647
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3972811638038886076,
            "blockIdx": 14
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シリウスシンボリ",
            "enName": "Sirius Symboli",
            "jpText": "……。",
            "enText": "…",
            "nextBlock": 16,
            "origClipLength": 48,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "――え！？",
                    "enText": "—Huh!",
                    "nextBlock": 16
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 80,
                    "pathId": -1939838216893979272
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 59,
                    "pathId": -4159498762210788304
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6155826070267809637,
            "blockIdx": 15
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シリウスシンボリ",
            "enName": "Sirius Symboli",
            "jpText": "フッ、ハハッ、ハハハッ！\r\nそんなに警戒すんなよ。\n別に取って食ったりはしねぇさ。",
            "enText": "Ha, ha, ha, ha! Don't be so cautious. It's \nnot like I'm going to take it and eat it.",
            "nextBlock": 17,
            "origClipLength": 98,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 89,
                    "pathId": 8771341610985652706
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 109,
                    "pathId": -7945156229657735035
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1958478651380943260,
            "blockIdx": 16
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シリウスシンボリ",
            "enName": "Sirius Symboli",
            "jpText": "……今は、な？",
            "enText": "… now, huh?",
            "nextBlock": -1,
            "origClipLength": 114,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 102,
                    "pathId": -2340900909677592248
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 102,
                    "pathId": 5733369806468634725
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7590751943383023058,
            "blockIdx": 17
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シリウスシンボリ",
            "enName": "Sirius Symboli",
            "jpText": "へぇ、素直ないい子だ。\r\nじゃあ、まずは前菜から――",
            "enText": "Heh, she's a nice, honest girl. Well, \nlet's start with a starter—",
            "nextBlock": 19,
            "origClipLength": 78,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 90,
                    "pathId": 1754645397091494572
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 89,
                    "pathId": 3460948009547156595
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8860045337280163281,
            "blockIdx": 18
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "そう言うと、シリウスシンボリは\r\n意味を教えつつ代わりに注文してくれた。\nすると――",
            "enText": "So Sirius-Simboli ordered it for me, telling \nme what it meant. Then—",
            "nextBlock": 20,
            "origClipLength": 99,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 110,
                    "pathId": 1340867622811754024
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 110,
                    "pathId": 612062884192553237
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2202135408999749923,
            "blockIdx": 19
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シリウスシンボリ",
            "enName": "Sirius Symboli",
            "jpText": "前菜にスープにメイン。\r\nなかなかいいバランスじゃねぇか。",
            "enText": "A starter, a soup and a main course. It's a \npretty good balance, isn't it?",
            "nextBlock": 21,
            "origClipLength": 82,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "教えてくれてありがとう！",
                    "enText": "Thanks for letting me know!",
                    "nextBlock": 21
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 164,
                    "pathId": -455576786844772743
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 175,
                    "pathId": 8907368695699731455
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 560040155821475493,
            "blockIdx": 20
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シリウスシンボリ",
            "enName": "Sirius Symboli",
            "jpText": "『ありがとう』？",
            "enText": "'Thank you'?",
            "nextBlock": 22,
            "origClipLength": 55,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 11,
                    "pathId": -3423352783514538490
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 66,
                    "pathId": 8003480024853910405
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7916029599461690717,
            "blockIdx": 21
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シリウスシンボリ",
            "enName": "Sirius Symboli",
            "jpText": "オイオイ……礼を言うのはちょっと\r\n早いんじゃないか？",
            "enText": "Oi oi… It's a bit early to \nbe thanking me, isn't it?",
            "nextBlock": 23,
            "origClipLength": 80,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "え？",
                    "enText": "Huh?",
                    "nextBlock": 23
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 38,
                    "pathId": -1209610179839809595
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 91,
                    "pathId": 1675769123444933312
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -4764055684755433717,
            "blockIdx": 22
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "どういうことかと考える間もなく、\r\n運ばれた料理をシリウスシンボリが\n自分のテーブルへ移していく。",
            "enText": "No sooner had she wondered what was \ngoing on, than Sirius-Simboris took \nthe food to her own table.",
            "nextBlock": 24,
            "origClipLength": 108,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 129,
                    "pathId": -1479769827505371889
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 158,
                    "pathId": -207320847921176931
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -478867372687709305,
            "blockIdx": 23
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シリウスシンボリ",
            "enName": "Sirius Symboli",
            "jpText": "残念だが、私は手本を見せただけだ。\r\nつまりこの料理は私のもの。",
            "enText": "I'm sorry, but I was just setting an \nexample. In other words, this dish is mine.",
            "nextBlock": 25,
            "origClipLength": 86,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "えぇ……",
                    "enText": "Yeah…",
                    "nextBlock": 25
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 103,
                    "pathId": -4258581756698017055
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 154,
                    "pathId": -1277981719067766256
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6537521880255148174,
            "blockIdx": 24
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シリウスシンボリ",
            "enName": "Sirius Symboli",
            "jpText": "ハハッ、そんな顔するなよ！\r\n……もっとからかいたくなるだろ？",
            "enText": "Hahaha, don't give me that look!… Makes you \nwant to tease me more, doesn't it?",
            "nextBlock": 26,
            "origClipLength": 85,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 95,
                    "pathId": -7830180490168218467
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 96,
                    "pathId": 2721923842648580988
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1980698722084447749,
            "blockIdx": 25
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シリウスシンボリ",
            "enName": "Sirius Symboli",
            "jpText": "さ、今度は自分で注文してみな。\r\n賢くなったかどうか、\nちゃんと見ててやるからよ。",
            "enText": "Now, go ahead and order for yourself. We'll \nsee if you're smart enough to do it.",
            "nextBlock": -1,
            "origClipLength": 98,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 69,
                    "pathId": -7249624655123456574
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 109,
                    "pathId": 4863881440022284317
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 2987251734959326416,
            "blockIdx": 26
        }
    ],
    "modified": 1669946377
}